professional dslr photo of a russian cyberpunk woman in her 40s with pink dyed hair with dark growth with curly pixie hairdo. The setting is sci-fi futuristic with strong cyberpunk elements. She is wearing a hi-tech body suit, small breastsed, probably military with carbon fiber elements and various sophisticated apparatuses and small texts and qr-codes. She also has some very intricate eyewear on one eye, probably an auto-targeting device.

In the background a rainy cyberpunk city at night with neo lights and holographic billboards.

She looks concentrated and you certainly don't want to mess with her.

High quality, high resolution, dramatic lighting, cinematic
